We have many years of dental experience for all your oral health needs.

Meet Dr. Paul Nguyen

Dr. Paul Nguyen is a Baton Rouge native and graduated from Catholic High School in 1998. He earned his Bachelor of Science degree from Louisiana State University and his Doctor of Dental Surgery degree from the University of Maryland Dental School. Dr. Nguyen stays current with modern technology and advances in dentistry to deliver dental treatment with improved efficiency, comfort, and outcomes.
